Nemo-iDeviceInfo
--------------------

Nemo-iDeviceInfo is a nemo extension showing extended device
information in the nemo properties dialog. It shows details like
serial number, software version, baseband/modem firmware version, and
storage usage (with nice eye candy).

Dependencies
------------
libimobiledevice - http://www.libimobiledevice.org/
libplist
libglib-2.0
libgtk+-2.0
libcairo
libpango
libpangocairo
libnemoextension

Optional Dependencies
---------------------
libgpod -- to enable detailled Audio/Video information

Installation
------------

Installation is simple. Just run:
$ ./autogen.sh
$ make && sudo make install

Source Code Repository:
	http://cgit.sukimashita.com/nemo-ideviceinfo.git/

README updated on:
	2010-03-21

